author: Dave Hooker
title: WATCH: Tennessee player stomps on UGA linebacker's helmet
text:
SEC Country
The Tennessee-Georgia game was a fiercely battled contest. However, it might have gone too far at one point, according to SEC Country .
>> RELATED: Gamecocks player after loss: 'Should (have) looked around like my parents said'
Watch here as a Tennessee player appears to purposefully step on a UGA player's head after a kickoff return. The Vols player appears to be freshman John Kelly, and the UGA player on the ground is junior linebacker Chuks Amaechi.
Tennessee went on to beat Georgia 38-31.
